title: Corpus Hermeticum T1 T2 (2007) (Soleil)cbr
description:
From the beginning of time, men sought to unravel the mysteries of creation. Mages, warlocks, shamans, alchemists... Many names of those, who secretly searched to reveal hidden secrets that make up the fabric of our universe. All this knowledge, which was believed lost forever, has been recorded by few chosen initiates in a mythical grimoire. This grail is called Corpus Hermeticum."
